    <title>言论自由（Freedom Of Speech）</title>
    <link href="https://pingmin.me/p/freedom-of-speech.html"/>
    <id>https://pingmin.me/p/freedom-of-speech.html</id>
    <published>2007-06-04T12:29:36.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-07-07T13:18:40.000Z</updated>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h2 id=&quot;宪法第三十五条-The-Article-35-of-Constitution-of-The-PRC&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#宪法第三十五条-The-Article-35-of-Constitution-of-The-PRC&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;宪法第三十五条 (The Article 35 of Constitution of The PRC)&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;宪法第三十五条 (The Article 35 of Constitution of The PRC)&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&quot;简体中文-Chinese-Simplified&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#简体中文-Chinese-Simplified&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;[简体中文 (Chinese Simplified)]&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;[简体中文 (Chinese Simplified)]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;中华人民共和国公民有言论、出版、集会、结社、游行、示威的自由。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;—— 《中华人民共和国宪法》第三十五条&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;English（英文）&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#English（英文）&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;[English（英文）]&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;[English（英文）]&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Citizens of the People’s Republic of China enjoy freedom of speech, of the press, of assembly, of association, of procession and of demonstration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;—— From Article 35, Constitution of The People’s Republic of China(People’s ROC, PRC)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
    
